These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  journalist, project-manager, musician, coach, bartender, software-developer
There are 6 different nationalities: indonesian, canadian, dutch, turkish, german, polish
1. the coach is on the left of the musician##1
2. the canadian is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the journalist is on the left of the project-manager##1
4. the german is between the software-developer and the indonesian##2
5. the turkish is between the german and the canadian##2
6. the indonesian is the coach##1
7. the bartender is on the left of the indonesian##1
8. the polish is on the left of the project-manager##1
9. the bartender is on the right of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Job           | journalist | project-manager | software-developer | bartender | coach    | musician  |
| Nationality   | polish | canadian   | turkish       | german        | indonesian | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different nationalities: indian, polish, russian, canadian, egyptian, british
6 different pets are kept: dog, bird, turtle, pony, ferret, fish
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the owner of the pony is between the canadian and the indian##2
4. the russian is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
5. the indian is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
7. the canadian is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
8. the polish is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Nationality   | polish | british | egyptian | canadian | russian | indian  |
| Pet           | fish | ferret  | dog | bird    | pony  | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
6 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, rat, turtle, fish, hamster
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, roller, motorbike, bike, train, snowmobile
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the person driving the airplane##2
7. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
9. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Pet         | ferret | mouse | hamster      | fish | turtle | rat      |
| Transport   | roller    | snowmobile  | airplane | bike   | train       | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
There 6 different types of food: potato, tomato, banana, cherry, pear, pumpkin
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, subway, train, skateboard, tram, helicopter
1. the person driving the train is the person eating cherry##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person eating banana##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating potato is the person driving the airplane##1
6. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the airplane and the person eating pumpkin##2
7. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
8. the person driving the train is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Food        | tomato    | pumpkin | banana | potato | pear | cherry   |
| Transport   | skateboard | tram        | subway  | airplane     | helicopter  | train |

