.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, thriller, spy, martial-arts, crime
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skiing, climbing, weightlifting, lacrosse, cricket, basketball
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | spy    | crime | thriller | documentary | martial-arts   |
| Sport         | cricket | skiing | weightlifting | basketball | lacrosse  | climbing |

