.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
There 6 different types of food: carrot, peach, zucchini, radish, tomato, plum
The people have 6 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, photography, cooking, writing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person eating peach##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
5. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person eating plum is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is the person eating plum##1
8. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating radish and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
9. the person eating carrot is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Food    | carrot | plum | tomato  | radish      | zucchini | peach  |
| Hobby   | hiking  | photography    | cooking | gardening | writing | fishing |

