.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: singing, drawing, writing, baking, camping, dancing
The people use 6 different means of transport: motorbike, train, helicopter, subway, car, scooter
1. the person driving the subway is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is baking##2
4. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the car##2
7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
9. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Hobby       | dancing | baking | singing | camping | writing | drawing |
| Transport   | helicopter | scooter    | car  | motorbike    | subway    | train    |

