.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  freelancer, security-guard, paramedic, firefighter, nurse, manager
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, salsa, pop, r&b, rock, country
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of country is between the fan of rock and the fan of classical##2
4. the firefighter is the fan of pop##1
5. the paramedic is between the security-guard and the nurse##2
6. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of country##1
7. the nurse is on the right of the manager##1
8. the nurse is on the right of the manager##1
9. the paramedic is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Job           | firefighter | manager | nurse | paramedic | security-guard | freelancer |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | r&b   | salsa         | classical    | country     | rock     |

