.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: writing, traveling, baking, fishing, magic-tricks, drawing
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cricket, weightlifting, badminton, basketball, ice-hockey, golf
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's sport is golf##2
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Hobby   | writing   | magic-tricks  | traveling | fishing | drawing | baking     |
| Sport   | weightlifting | cricket | golf    | ice-hockey | basketball | badminton |

