4. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the frog##1
5. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching romance movies##2
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
7. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
8. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the owner of the horse##2
9. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1

