.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle, horse, fish, hamster, bird
The people use 6 different means of transport: bus, boat, ship, snowmobile, helicopter, scooter
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the horse##2
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 8. the owner of the fish is the person driving the bus##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is between the person driving the bus and the owner of the turtle##2
10. the owner of the fish is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | bird   | hamster | horse       | fish | mouse    | turtle |
| Transport   | boat | helicopter  | ship | bus      | snowmobile | scooter        |

