.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  musician, lawyer, librarian, journalist, electrician, scientist
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, western, epic, adventure, zombie
 1. the librarian is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the lawyer is the person watching epic movies##1
 4. the librarian is between the journalist and the person watching zombie movies##2
 5. the person watching western movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the electrician##2
 6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the musician##1
 7. the lawyer is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the musician##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is the musician##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Job           | lawyer      | journalist | librarian | musician   | scientist  | electrician |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | disaster  | fantasy             | zombie | western | adventure       |

