5. the person eating spinach is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
6. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of techno##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is the person eating potato##1
8. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
