.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-16::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, water, lemonade, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: baseball, golf, sailing, basketball, ice-hockey, surfing
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person drinking 7up##2
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate   | mirinda   | water        | 7up   | almond-milk        | lemonade   |
| Sport      | baseball | ice-hockey | basketball | sailing | surfing | golf |

