5. the fan of trance is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of soul##2
6. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
7. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
9. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |       5       |   6    |
