.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: magic-tricks, sudoku, writing, reading, traveling, hiking
There are 6 different nationalities: nigerian, colombian, egyptian, canadian, brazilian, american
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 2. the nigerian is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the canadian is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
 6. the american is on the right of the canadian##1
 7. the colombian is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the egyptian is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Hobby         | reading | magic-tricks | sudoku | hiking | traveling | writing |
| Nationality   | nigerian | brazilian | egyptian      | canadian     | american       | colombian |

 